        "subject": "LU-3044 llite: LSeek SEEK_CUR incorrect after O_APPEND write",
        "message": "LU-3044 llite: LSeek SEEK_CUR incorrect after O_APPEND write\n\nWhen a file is opened for writing with O_APPEND set and data\nis written, the offset in the file is incorrect after the write.\nIt is too large by approximately the size of the write.\n\nThis does not cause data corruption because VFS resets the\noffset to end of file before each write when O_APPEND is set.\n\nThis is resolved by removing the change made for BUG:17711.\nThis is being pushed for testing - A commit message with\nmore detail is waiting on an update to LU-3044 from\nJinshan Xiong.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I0b262c77b6c54b864264a00314c98d178bb154c3\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
